{"tid":1624701,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解唔可以幫美心裝修?","createTime":"2019-10-05T04:37:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T14:30:11.000Z","uid":54641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4447b2da24bb3470e249e3c65dcd7e900b36f144","tid":1624701,"uid":54641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:37:43.000Z","msg":"成堆帶風向POST話乜都唔做得 咁係示威定示弱?咩叫行動升級?<br />\n依家先黎話會影響市民生活? 和理塞就唔影響咩 帶風向POST都千幾正評<br />\n<br />\n睇返伍淑清係聯合國講左咩:<br />\n<br />\n&quot;聯合國人權理事會在瑞士日內瓦召開，議程包括香港問題。香港各界婦女聯合協進會主席何超瓊和監察顧問伍淑清將發表演講。何超瓊在會前表示，暴力示威者過去三個月破壞市民的平和生活，她們希望在國際場合說出真實的香港現狀和大眾的真實想法，冀西方國家和香港年輕人能夠正視中國的發展。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n核爆都唔割"},{"pid":"aa26f7e0f83619d5ef41f9d650f57147022d0674","tid":1624701,"uid":54641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:40:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae2c89f599b9401cbe017cada43f3694a4e0d29c","tid":1624701,"uid":54641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:46:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b93b43ea2fa3bcc012410d6de7c55ad070cfd1e8","tid":1624701,"uid":54641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:54:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa36bdf56a26a5308ce3bfd3f322d0b948e4745b","tid":1624701,"uid":54966,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:56:34.000Z","msg":"因為人地已經跪低左<br />\n個所謂太子女根本股份好小<br />\n罷食已經夠"},{"pid":"741ec87853130bd2776e635659deaa7c9fbd679f","tid":1624701,"uid":294343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:07:28.000Z","msg":"而且仲有更大問題嘅企業，例如地產商，福建邦"},{"pid":"659e8a37815f254c99eb05952584820fa5a59532","tid":1624701,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:30:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZANn4pK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail